# CalorieCam Deployment
## Rule Type: Always

### Backend (Railway):
- Auto-deploy via GitHub Actions on push to `main`.
- Environment variables stored securely on Railway (GPT-4o keys, Supabase URL/keys).

### Mobile App (Expo):
- OTA updates via Expo on merge to `main`.
- Optional EAS builds for App Store/Play Store.

### Storage (Supabase):
- Store images securely via Supabase Storage bucket.
- Images linked via URLs stored in Supabase tables.